info.name: SGGW MeetApp v0.5
info.description:
# SGGW MEET_APP REST API

This collection contains all the requests used in the SGGW MEET_APP backend REST API and should serve as a reference for manual testing of the API.

## Environments

This collection contains two environments:

- `dev` to be used by app developers when running the API locally (e.g. using symfony server)
- `prod` to be used by all other users for testing the API which is running on a remote server
    

If API won't work for you please check that you have the correct environment enabled. If despite having the correct environment you are receiving errors, please report them to app's developers.
